To the esteemed Arch-Mage Trebonius Artorius, Guildmaster of Vvardenfell,
Upon receiving this letter, you will step down from your post and grant the title of Arch-Mage to <Name>. From this day forward, <Name> will handle all Guild matters in Vvardenfell. You may keep the title of Arch-Mage, but you will retire from active participation in the affairs of the Guild.
In the Emperor's Name,
Ocato